name: Ombré Bundles
description:
For the ladies who would like to enhance their look by adding some color. Ombré means to lighten the ends of the hair gradually, the color should fade as it extends down to the ends of the hair. Remember that the pricing is per bundle. 
*Example: if you order three bundles of hair you need to add this option to your cart three times if you want all three bundles colored.
*Ombré option includes getting the hair washed, conditioned, and lightening the ends
If you would like to have your bundles dyed a specific color please use the contact information to express your needs. Also remember the price for dye is per bundle. Dying the bundles includes a wash and conditioning treatment prior to applying the color.
Color Lift is an option for ladies who want their hair a lighter shade of brown, you will receive a wash, and condition with this option in addition to your color lift.

Also take advantage of getting your hair deep conditioned, and your wefts sealed before delivery this will save you the hassle of doing it. You only have to worry about the installation

name: Peruvian Body Wave
description: As one of our top sellers, I love to offer this hair. Peruvian body wave provides that exotic look you are going for. The hair has a soft texture and is easy to manage. The hair has a medium about of body, if you want a bigger look you and curl it to your liking or add try adding more packs of hair.

name: Brazilian Straight
description: This hair is one the top sellers due to the low level of shedding and tangling. This hair is silky to the touch and gives the straight look you going for extra volume. This hair curls beautifully. And you do not have to worry about burning the hair.

name: Brazilian Body Wave
description: This hair is a top seller due to it's great quality, and luster. The bundles are thick and will easily provide a full look to your hairstyle. The hair can be washed and dyed. You can apply heat to the hair. It will straighten beautifully and it curls nicely. The curl pattern will return after the hair has been washed. Hair can last up to a year when properly taken care of.
